# CVE-2026-2100: p11-kit NULL dereference (HIGH, fixed in 0.26.2-r0)
#
# Suppressed because: the fix exists in Alpine's package repos but is not
# yet published in the eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine base image. Patching
# it via `apk upgrade` in the Dockerfile requires executing Alpine's sh
# inside an ARM64 container during cross-compilation, which fails under
# Docker Desktop's DooD QEMU emulation on this amd64 build host. The
# suppression will be removed once the base image is updated to include the
# fix (i.e. when `apk info p11-kit` inside the image returns >= 0.26.2-r0).
CVE-2026-2100
